@Section Examples
@InsertChunk FinQuiver

@Chapter Path Categories

Path categories are categories whose objects are the objects of a quiver and whose morphisms
are paths in the quiver. A path is a sequence of composable morphisms in the quiver.

@Section GAP categories
@Section Constructors
@Section Attributes
@Section Operations

@Section Examples
